text: Agdistis glaseri is a moth in the family Pterophoridae. It is known from Spain. The wingspan is 24–26 mm. The forewings are grey and the hindwings are white.Agdistis-Arten Aus Spanien (Lep, Pterophoridae) ==References== Category:Agdistinae Category:Moths described in 1978
title: Agdistis glaseri
